  "texts": [
    "Since the research was inductive, no key concepts or theories guided the analysis.",
    "Given the inductive approach, we did not use holdout data.",
    "There was not an overwhelming amount of text to analyze and the researchers were able to read all the text, so ChatGPT was enlisted as a supervised virtual research assistant whose thematic coding could augment and supplement the researcher's own reading and interpretation, but could also be rejected or dismissed by the researchers based on their reasoned engagement with the texts.",
    "In essence, we use LLMs to extend thematic coding by identifying themes we might miss in our own reading, and act as a robustness check by corroborating what we did observe.",
    "We also take advantage of ChatGPT's chat function to create more abstract restatements of the themes that can assist us in the thematic analysis, both in terms of \"seeing\" what each document contains, but also when it comes to identifying patterns across documents."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
